OL,3,CNominations open for Pride of Britain
OL,4,C2026
OL,6,FNominations for the Daily Mirror's
OL,7,FPride of Britain Awards are now open,
OL,8,Fand we are hunting for Channel's ITV
OL,9,FRegional Fundraiser of the Year.
OL,11,FThe awards are one of the biggest
OL,12,Fevents in Britain's showbiz calendar -
OL,13,Funiquely bringing together celebrities
OL,14,Fwith the nation's unsung heroes for a
OL,15,Fnight of glitz and glamour.
OL,17,FITV's Regional Fundraiser of the Year
OL,18,FAward celebrates those extraordinary
OL,19,Fpeople who've gone above and beyond
OL,20,Ffor the Channel Islands.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
