OL,3,CNominations open for Pride of Britain
OL,4,C2026
OL,6,FThis could be any person or group who
OL,7,Fhas fundraised any amount of money -
OL,8,Fbig or small - for local causes.
OL,10,FThey might have done a one-off event,
OL,11,For they may have dedicated a
OL,12,Fsignificant amount of time over
OL,13,Fseveral years to their fundraising
OL,14,Fefforts.
OL,16,FThey might have a particularly
OL,17,Femotional story to tell, or perhaps
OL,18,Ftheir fundraising efforts were
OL,19,Fespecially creative or unusual.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
