OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781269896
OL,3,CNominations open for Pride of Britain
OL,4,C2026
OL,6,FFrom the nominees, four regional
OL,7,Ffinalists will be selected - and the
OL,8,Fwinner will be invited to attend the
OL,9,FPride of Britain Awards ceremony to
OL,10,Frepresent the islands.
OL,12,FLast year, Jo Priaulx from Guernsey
OL,13,Fwon the Regional Fundraiser of the
OL,14,FYear Award in the Channel Islands.
OL,16,FIn 2025, Jo raised around #35,000 for
OL,17,Fher charity, the Priaulx Premature
OL,18,FBaby Foundation, which she founded
OL,19,Ffollowing the premature births of her
OL,20,Ftwo children.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
